      "created": 1679197273,
      "updated": 1679197273
    },
    {
      "id": "64168458e600350000e89399",
      "text": "　[https://dictionary.goo.ne.jp/word/孫子/ 孫子（まごこ）の意味・使い方をわかりやすく解説 - goo国語辞書]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1679197273,
      "updated": 1679197273
    },
    {
      "id": "64168458e600350000e8939a",
      "text": " >１ 孫と子。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1679197273,
      "updated": 1679197273
    },
    {
